(default)
Enum cef_urlrequest_status_t

   in cef_types.h

Flags that represent CefURLRequest status.

Field Summary
UR_CANCELED
          Request was canceled programatically.
UR_FAILED
          Request failed for some reason.
UR_HANDLED_EXTERNALLY
          Request was successful but was handled by an external program, so there is no response data.
UR_IO_PENDING
          An IO request is pending, and the caller will be informed when it is completed.
UR_SUCCESS
          Request succeeded.
UR_UNKNOWN = 0
          Unknown status.
 

Field Detail

UR_CANCELED

public UR_CANCELED
Request was canceled programatically.

UR_FAILED

public UR_FAILED
Request failed for some reason.

UR_HANDLED_EXTERNALLY

public UR_HANDLED_EXTERNALLY
Request was successful but was handled by an external program, so there is no response data. This usually means the current page should not be navigated, but no error should be displayed.

UR_IO_PENDING

public UR_IO_PENDING
An IO request is pending, and the caller will be informed when it is completed.

UR_SUCCESS

public UR_SUCCESS
Request succeeded.

UR_UNKNOWN

public UR_UNKNOWN = 0
Unknown status.
